OL,5,ESUMMER HOLIDAYSGby Tracy Stringer, 12, 
OL,6, Graveney School, Tooting, London       
OL,7,BThe summer holiday is here             
OL,8,BHip hip hooray!                        
OL,9,BWe can have more sleep now that school 
OL,10,Bis out of the way.                     
OL,11,BWe can go to the pool and play catch   
OL,12,Bwith our ball.                         
OL,13,BWe can do what we like without a       
OL,14,Bthought about school.                  
OL,15,BWe will go to the cinema to watch a    
OL,16,Bfilm about bees.                       
OL,17,BBut at the same time we think that     
OL,18,Bmoney grows on trees!                  
